Name: Amount paid
Description: What the customer has already paid.

Name: Amount remaining
Description: What the customer will pay in the future.

Name: Close date
Description: Date the record is "closed".

Name: Created by user ID
Description: The user who created this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Create date
Description: The date and time at which this object was created. This value is automatically set by HubSpot and may not be modified.

Name: Description
Description: Overview/explanation of the project's purpose and goals
Usages: Automation platform flow (3); Object requirement (1); Properties v3 card (1)

Name: Last Activity Date
Description: The last time a note, call, email, meeting, or task was logged for a project. This is updated automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Last modified date
Description: Most recent timestamp of any property update for this object. This includes HubSpot internal properties, which can be visible or hidden. This property is updated automatically.

Name: Merged record IDs
Description: The list of record IDs that have been merged into this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Name
Description: Title of the project
Usages: Automation platform flow (4); Object requirement (1); Report (1); Dataset (1); Sales view (4)

Name: Next Activity Date
Description: The date of the next upcoming activity for a project. This property is set automatically by HubSpot based on user action. This includes logging a future call, sales email, or meeting using the Log feature, as well as creating a future task or scheduling a future meeting. This is updated automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Record ID
Description: The unique ID for this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Record source detail 1
Description: First level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 2
Description: Second level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source detail 3
Description: Third level of detail on how this record was created.

Name: Record source
Description: How this record was created.

Name: Pipeline
Description: The pipeline that contains this project
Usages: Automation platform flow (4); Object requirement (1); Sales view (2); Properties v3 card (1)

Name: Pipeline Stage
Description: The pipeline stage that contains this project
Usages: Calculated property (1); Rollup property (1); Inbounddb lists (1); Automation platform flow (15); Object requirement (1); Report (2); Dataset (2); Sales view (4); Properties v3 card (1); Association v3 card (1)

Name: Priority
Description: Importance or urgency level of the project

Name: Project Tags
Description: Tags associated with your project

Name: Shared teams
Description: Additional teams whose users can access the record based on their permissions. This can be set manually or through Workflows or APIs.

Name: Shared users
Description: Additional users that can access the record based on their permissions. This can be set manually or through Workflows and APIs.

Name: Start date
Description: Day the project starts being worked on
Usages: Calculated property (3); Rollup property (1); Automation platform flow (4); Object requirement (1); Report (1); Sales view (4); Properties v3 card (1); Association v3 card (1)

Name: Status
Description: This represents how the project is tracking relative towards expectations.
Options: On Track (on_track); Delayed (delayed); Blocked (blocked); Completed (completed); On-Hold (on_hold); At-Risk (at_risk)
Usages: Rollup property (1); Automation platform flow (5); Object requirement (1); Report (3); Dataset (1); Sales view (4); Properties v3 card (1); Association v3 card (1)

Name: Target due date
Description: Date the project is anticipated to be completed
Usages: Automation platform flow (4); Object requirement (1); Report (2); Dataset (2); Sales view (1); Properties v3 card (1)

Name: Target Duration
Description: Calculates the time between the start date and target date. If the start date occurs after the target date, the value returned is 0.

Name: Total cost
Description: The total monetary value of the project

Name: Type
Description: A drop down or multi-select field where customers can differentiate among varied types of project
Usages: Automation platform flow (4); Properties v3 card (1)

Name: Updated by user ID
Description: The user who last updated this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Owner assigned date
Description: The most recent timestamp of when an owner was assigned to this record. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Owner
Description: The owner of the object.
Usages: Automation platform flow (7); Object requirement (1); Sales view (3); Properties v3 card (1)

Name: Owner's main team
Description: The main team of the record owner. This value is set automatically by HubSpot.

Name: Target Launch Date
Usages: Rollup property (1); Automation platform flow (4); Object requirement (1); Dataset (2); Sales view (3); Properties v3 card (1); Association v3 card (1)
